Dante Basco https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dante_Basco 0 Dante R. Basco (born August 29, 1975) is an American actor, voice actor and dancer known for his role as Rufio, leader of the Lost Boys in the 1991 movie Hook as well as his voice-over work in films, TV shows and video games.
